<p>Thank you for
    <% if @user.donations.active.any? %>
    donating <%= pluralize @user.donations.active.count, 'book' %> so far
    <% else %>
    signing up to donate books
    <% end %>
    through Free Objectivist Books!
</p>

<p>On <%= l @pledge.created_at.to_date, format: :short %>, you pledged to donate <%= @pledge.quantity %> books.
    Right now there are <%= format_number @request_count %> students waiting for books.
</p>

<p><strong><%= link_to 'Read their appeals and choose students to donate to', donate_url %></strong></p>
